thread.title: Sarah

author: Sarah
title: Sarah
text:
Really easy process...would defo do this again.
My only real feedback for improvement is to review the $33 transaction fee, understand as "middle men" you need to make money but I am guessing you are charging the seller and buyer similar fees so this adds up to a hefty % commission rate. Something around the $15 - 20 mark would be a lot more appropriate especially as I think I also got charged $5 or $6 to print my own ticket!
